OL,3,CDad who lost son in car park fall
OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,FThe dad of a teenager who died after
OL,7,Ffalling from a multi-storey car park
OL,8,Fsays he is "confident" the Government
OL,9,Fis considering his calls for a change
OL,10,Fin the law "very closely".
OL,12,FGabriel Santer was 15-years-old when
OL,13,Fhe fell from the top of a multi-storey
OL,14,Fcar park in October 2020.
OL,16,FHe had been with friends at the Q-car
OL,17,Fpark, in Liverpool city centre, and
OL,18,Fhad just texted his mum to tell her
OL,19,Fwhat he wanted for tea, but never came
OL,20,Fhome.
