OL,3,CDad who lost son in car park fall
OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,FSince then, his dad Johnny Santer has
OL,7,Fcampaigned to increase the minimum
OL,8,Fheight of barriers on top of car parks
OL,9,Fthrough the Multi-Storey Car Parks
OL,10,F(Safety) Bill, known as Gabe's Law.
OL,11,FThe bill was introduced to parliament
OL,12,Fin February by the family's MP, Maria
OL,13,FEagle.
OL,15,FFollowing that, the Prime Minister Sir
OL,16,FKeir Starmer promised to review safety
OL,17,Fstandards in multi-stories to "prevent
OL,18,Ffuture tragedies."
