OL,3,CDad who lost son in car park fall
OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,FThis week, Mr Santer met with the new
OL,7,FBuilding Safety Minister, in what he
OL,8,Fdescribed as "very, very positive"
OL,9,Fexchange.
OL,11,FSamantha Dixon MP informed Mr Santer
OL,12,Fthat the Government is launching a
OL,13,Fpublic call for evidence, followed by
OL,14,Fa 12-week consultation period.
OL,16,F"We're urging any other families, any
OL,17,Fother community members that's been
OL,18,Faffected in similar circumstances to
OL,19,Fget in touch with their MP - let them
OL,20,Fknow how it's affected them," Mr
OL,21,FSanter said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
