OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,FAt an inquest into Gabriel's death, a
OL,7,Fcoroner recorded an open conclusion.
OL,9,FA Q-Park statement said: "The death of
OL,10,FGabriel Santer is a tragedy and we are
OL,11,Fdeeply sorry for their loss and have
OL,12,Fexpressed this to the Santer family
OL,13,Fdirectly.
OL,15,F"We take safety at our sites extremely
OL,16,Fseriously, which is why the Hanover
OL,17,FStreet car park outperformed required
OL,18,Fbuilding regulations. Additionally, an
OL,19,Findependent panel has determined no
OL,20,Fwrongdoing on the part of Q-Park in
OL,21,Fthese tragic circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
