OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,F"Whilst we are understanding and
OL,7,Fsympathetic with the motivations
OL,8,Fbehind proposals for further
OL,9,Fsafeguarding of high level structures,
OL,10,Fwe regret that several inaccuracies
OL,11,Fare being put forward in Parliament
OL,12,Fabout Q-Park that undermine these good
OL,13,Fintentions.
OL,15,F"The British Parking Association
OL,16,Frepresents the industry and will, we
OL,17,Fare sure, welcome constructive and
OL,18,Fgenuine dialogue with Parliamentarians
OL,19,Fand all interested parties."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
