OL,4,C'confident' the Government is listening
OL,6,FA statement from The British Parking
OL,7,FAssociation (BPA) said: "We have
OL,8,Foffered to work with Maria Eagle
OL,9,Fbecause we support the essence of this
OL,10,Fbill.
OL,12,F"The BPA is already actively working
OL,13,Fwith Government in the wider review of
OL,14,FBuilding Regulations.
OL,16,F"Additionally, we publish advice and
OL,17,Fguidance to members on many aspects of
OL,18,Fcar park design, including preventing
OL,19,Ffalls from multi-story parking
OL,20,Ffacilities.
